## Setup

### Download for Windows

Server at `https://dl.min.io/server/minio/release/windows-amd64/minio.exe`

Client at `https://dl.minio.io/client/mc/release/windows-amd64/mc.exe`

### Create a directory for minio data

```cmd
mkdir C:\minio\data
```

### Start minio service

```cmd
minio.exe server C:\minio\data --console-address ":9001"
```

By default:

- RootUser: minioadmin

- RootPass: minioadmin

To change the root user name and password, set the environment variables before starting the service.

```cmd
set MINIO_ROOT_USER=minioadmin
set MINIO_ROOT_PASSWORD=minioadmin123
```

### File management via MinIO Client (mc)

Add your local MinIO as an alias

```cmd
mc.exe alias set local http://127.0.0.1:9000 minioadmin minioadmin
```

Create a bucket

```
mc.exe mb local/content-search
```

Upload files into the bucket

```
mc.exe cp C:\path\to\file.pdf local/content-search/

mc.exe cp --recursive C:\path\to\docs local/content-search/docs
```

List the bucket files
```
mc.exe ls local/content-search
```



